Package model

Class Alien

java.lang.Object
model.Alien
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlienType1, AlienType2, AlienType3
public class Alien extends Object
The Alien class represents an alien object in a game. It contains methods to move the alien, shoot bullets, and retrieve its image.
